<div class="col-span-full lg:col-start-4 [&+&]:mt-15 rich-text-block
  lg:col-span-6
  ">

          
        
        <div class="wysiwyg rich-text-content col-span-full ">
      <p>We believe the most important decision a philanthropist makes is choosing which causes to fund.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">That&#8217;s why we devote significant effort to investigating specific areas before committing resources to them. We </span>evaluate causes using three key criteria:</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>Importance<br />
</strong>The scale and severity of the problem</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>Neglectedness<br />
</strong>Whether the cause receives adequate attention and resources</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>Tractability<br />
</strong>The likelihood that additional resources can create meaningful progress</p>

    </div>
    
        
  </div>                            
